                                            <div class="relative h-64 lg:h-96 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
                                                {% for image in validLocalImages %}
                                                    <div class="hidden duration-700 ease-in-out" data-carousel-item>
                                                        <img src="{{ asset(vich_uploader_asset(image, 'image')) }}" class="absolute block w-full h-full object-cover -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 top-1/2 left-1/2" alt="{{ image.title }}">
                                                    </div>
                                                {% endfor %}
                                            </div>
                                            <!-- Indicateurs -->
                                            <div class="absolute z-30 flex -translate-x-1/2 bottom-5 left-1/2 space-x-3">
                                                {% for i in 0..validLocalImages|length-1 %}
                                                    <button type="button" class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-white/50 hover:bg-white" aria-current="{{ i == 0 ? 'true' : 'false' }}" data-carousel-slide-to="{{ i }}"></button>
                                                {% endfor %}
                                            </div>
                                            <!-- Contrôles -->
                                            <button type="button" class="absolute top-0 start-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center h-full px-4 cursor-pointer group" data-carousel-prev>
                                                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/30 group-focus:ring-4 group-focus:ring-white">
                                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white rtl:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 6 10">
                                                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 1 1 5l4 4"/>
                                                    </svg>
                                                </span>
                                            </button>
                                            <button type="button" class="absolute top-0 end-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center h-full px-4 cursor-pointer group" data-carousel-next>
                                                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/30 group-focus:ring-4 group-focus:ring-white">
                                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white rtl:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 6 10">
                                                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m1 9 4-4-4-4"/>
                                                    </svg>
                                                </span>
                                            </button>
                                        </div>
                                    {% endif %}
                                {% else %}
                                    <div class="h-64 lg:h-96 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                        <p class="text-gray-500">Images des locaux non disponibles</p>
                                    </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            {% else %}
                                <div class="h-64 lg:h-96 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <p class="text-gray-500">Images des locaux non disponibles</p>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Texte -->
                        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-justify">Créé en 2021, Be Elle vous accueille dans un cadre chaleureux et épuré pour sublimer et prendre soin de vos ongles. Je serais ravie de vous recevoir en prestation pour sublimer vos ongles ou lors d'une formation afin de vous transmettre mon savoir ainsi que ma passion. N'hésitez pas à me contacter pour toute question, ou information.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section Nos Prestations -->
        <div class="mb-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                <div class="px-6 py-4 border-b border-gray-200">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">💅 Nos Prestations</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                        <!-- Image -->
                        <div>
                            {% if homeImages.prestations is not empty %}
                                {% set validPrestationsImages = homeImages.prestations|filter(image => image.imageName) %}
                                {% if validPrestationsImages|length > 0 %}
                                    {% if validPrestationsImages|length == 1 %}
                                        {% set prestationsImage = validPrestationsImages|first %}
                                        <div class="h-64 lg:h-96 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                                            <img src="{{ asset(vich_uploader_asset(prestationsImage, 'image')) }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="Nos prestations">
                                        </div>
                                    {% else %}
                                        <!-- Carrousel pour les prestations -->
                                        <div id="prestations-carousel" class="relative w-full" data-carousel="slide">
                                            <div class="relative h-64 lg:h-96 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
                                                {% for image in validPrestationsImages %}
                                                    <div class="hidden duration-700 ease-in-out" data-carousel-item>
                                                        <img src="{{ asset(vich_uploader_asset(image, 'image')) }}" class="absolute block w-full h-full object-cover -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 top-1/2 left-1/2" alt="{{ image.title }}">
                                                    </div>
                                                {% endfor %}
                                            </div>
                                            <!-- Indicateurs -->
                                            <div class="absolute z-30 flex -translate-x-1/2 bottom-5 left-1/2 space-x-3">
                                                {% for i in 0..validPrestationsImages|length-1 %}
                                                    <button type="button" class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-white/50 hover:bg-white" aria-current="{{ i == 0 ? 'true' : 'false' }}" data-carousel-slide-to="{{ i }}"></button>
                                                {% endfor %}
                                            </div>
                                            <!-- Contrôles -->
                                            <button type="button" class="absolute top-0 start-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center h-full px-4 cursor-pointer group" data-carousel-prev>
                                                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/30 group-focus:ring-4 group-focus:ring-white">
                                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white rtl:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 6 10">
                                                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 1 1 5l4 4"/>
                                                    </svg>
                                                </span>
                                            </button>
                                            <button type="button" class="absolute top-0 end-0 z-30 flex items-center justify-center h-full px-4 cursor-pointer group" data-carousel-next>
                                                <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/30 group-focus:ring-4 group-focus:ring-white">
                                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white rtl:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 6 10">
                                                        <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m1 9 4-4-4-4"/>
                                                    </svg>
                                                </span>
                                            </button>
                                        </div>
                                    {% endif %}
                                {% else %}
                                    <div class="h-64 lg:h-96 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                        <p class="text-gray-500">Images des prestations non disponibles</p>
                                    </div>
                                {% endif %}
                            {% else %}
                                <div class="h-64 lg:h-96 rounded-lg bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <p class="text-gray-500">Images des prestations non disponibles</p>
                                </div>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Texte -->
                        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-justify mb-6">Spécialiste du traitement de l'ongle naturel, Be Elle vous propose une large gamme de prestations pour sublimer vos ongles sans les abîmer. Soucieux de votre santé, nous n'utilisons donc pas de colle pour nos prestations. Dans la même dynamique nous n'utilisons que du matériel stérilisé selon les normes en vigueur du métier. Dans toutes nos prestations est incluse la manucure russe sans douleur, qui permet un travail poussé des cuticules pour une pose durable. Que ce soit sur ongles naturels ou pas, Be Elle vous offre des manucures luxueuses et durables 3 semaines minimum.</p>
                            <div class="flex">
                                <a href="{{ path('app_prestation_index') }}" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
